The paper deals with deep learning for scene understanding and localization, which is a common topic in computer vision (cs.CV) and robotics (cs.RO). The paper also proposes a novel architecture for multitask learning, which is a popular area of research in machine learning (cs.LG) and artificial intelligence (cs.AI). Additionally, the paper discusses semantic features and self-supervised learning, which are also relevant to natural language processing (cs.CL).
